data.description: Exquisite 4BD, 2.5BA Two-Story in Bel Moore Subdivision! Spacious home, boasting a sleek kitchen with stainless steel appliances, tiled backsplash, and flooring. Luxurious Primary Suite features vaulted ceiling, walk-in closet, and spa-like ensuite with double sinks, claw foot tub, and separate shower. Enjoy elegant wood floors throughout. Nestled on a private lot with fenced yard, sprawling deck, firepit, garden, and storage shed. Cozy up in the spacious living room with a charming fireplace. Don't miss this gem!
